"about_title" = "About Developer";
"about_message" = "The original goal of making this app was simple: to help Pikmin Bloom players connect with each other more easily. Whether it is teaming up for mushroom battles or exchanging postcards, I hope it makes interacting with other players more convenient.\n\nThe idea for \"honey\" in the app comes from Pikmin Bloom's flower-planting concept. Since everyone is already planting flowers, it felt like bees should be the ones encouraging connection and exchange. That is why you receive honey when you interact with other players.\n\nI hope this small tool helps everyone enjoy the game a little more. If you have any suggestions or run into any issues, feel free to contact me through Gmail or send feedback from within the app.";
